        "text_z6d7GK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Welcome to Cook & Bathe – Melbourne’s trusted destination for premium kitchens, bathrooms and renovation supplies. As a proud family-owned business with over 30 years of experience, we combine industry expertise with personalised service to help you create spaces you’ll love. We believe kitchens and bathrooms are the heart of every home, so our curated range features only the highest-quality products from leading Australian and international brands. With three Melbourne showrooms and a seamless online store, our team is here to guide you from inspiration to installation, ensuring every project is stylish, functional and built to last.</p>",
