        "text_DtBxCM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Comprehensive Product Range:</strong> From tapware, showers, vanities, and baths to kitchen appliances, sinks, ovens, and more, we stock products suited to every style, budget, and need. You can browse by room, brand, colour, price or design style.  </p><p><strong>Trusted Brands:</strong> We partner with well-known and reliable names like Phoenix, Hansgrohe, Smeg, Franke and others to ensure quality, performance, and design excellence.  </p><p><strong>Showrooms & Inspiration:</strong> Visit our Melbourne showrooms (Flemington, Fawkner, Burwood)<em> </em>to see products in real spaces. Get inspired, test finishes, and imagine what your renovated kitchen or bathroom could become.  </p><p><strong>Design & Support:</strong> It’s not just about products. With decades of experience, our team helps you with knowledge, guidance, and after-sales support, making your renovation or build smoother.  </p>"
          }
        }
