        "description": "<p> Cook & Bathe are a family-run business with over 30 years of experience providing wholesale bathroom supplies in Melbourne as well as laundry and kitchen accessories.</p><p>In 2005 the family refocused on the kitchen and bathroom as central points of the home, which has led to the creation of Cook & Bathe as a provider of tailored bathrooms and kitchen designs. Find products online or visit the bathroom and kitchen showroom in Flemington to benefit from the team’s extensive experience and knowledge.<br/>        </p>"
