            "text": "<p>At Cook & Bathe, customer service is at the heart of everything we do, and we recognize its utmost importance in building strong and lasting relationships with our valued customers.</p><p>Our commitment lies in creating the best experience for each individual who walks through our doors. We take pride in offering expert knowledge and advice, guiding our customers through their decision-making process to find the perfect solutions for their specific needs. Whether they are revamping their Kitchen, Bathroom or Laundry, our team is dedicated to providing the necessary inspiration and ideas to fuel their creativity and turn their vision into reality.</p>",
