    "4f013501-2a37-469b-a155-b2f490e0b28b": {
      "type": "cb-about-content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "2271ca84-a954-47b9-a625-f7e057da05cb": {
          "type": "box",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/about-odd-small-img.png",
            "content": "<p>The bathroom is where we both begin and end our day, so Cook & Bathe guides its customers through forming bathroom designs that aim to create a sanctuary within the home. A suite of bathroom accessories from Australian and international brands – including Villeroy and Boch, Caroma, Phoenix Tapware, and more – allows you to indulge in the process of creating a luxury retreat.</p>"
          }
        },
        "b5c99eb4-6a1f-4eb3-83d4-ecc2294b27cc": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/about-content-img.png"
          }
        },
        "b26b5f18-616c-4c91-80af-a79c6dd46574": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The kitchen is the modern day fireplace, a communal space around which we gather and connect over a common love for food. Cook & Bathe works with kitchen appliances from Smeg, Euro Appliances, Kleenmaid and other renowned brands to create fitted kitchens that offer a seamless cooking experience, turning the everyday cook into a professional chef. Their process of forming an ideal kitchen design focuses on the interplay of functionality with form to create a space in which the act of cooking centralises the kitchen’s role within the home.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
